experience.description: Working as a Software Developer dedicated to creating and innovating trending as well as unique mobile and web applications.

projects.name: Offar
projects.description: Offar was an Online Shopping site and was developed using PDO. It was helpful to compare offers among various shops at Kannur.

projects.name: Auditorium
projects.description: Auditorium was a management project developed using Codeigniter. It manages all aspects related to an auditorium such as Booking, Scheduling, Billing, Cancellations etc.

projects.name: GDiary
projects.description: GDiary was a project developed in Laravel to manage all aspects of a firm such as Company creations, Hiring Staffs, Salary management, GST billing, Transaction management, Estimations etc.

projects.name: Chitty
projects.description: Chitty is a mobile application developed with Android Java for people in a particular locality. It has phases like admin, agents, and users, providing reports like ledger, draw details, and payments.

projects.name: OnReach
projects.description: OnReach is a mobile application developed with Flutter Dart for school or college staff to record each student's examination marks in a class.
